                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18431023-2831-offence-1 t18431023-cd-9"></join>23rd of Sept</rs>., 1 looking-glass and stand, value 8<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18431023-name-149" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-149" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
