                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18431023-2831-offence-1 t18431023-name-149"></join>Edward John Gairdner</persName>; and that Jones had been before convicted of felony.</rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18431023-name-150" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-150" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-150" type="surname" value="HORNE"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-150" type="given" value="JAMES"></interp>JAMES HORNE</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Tottenham-court-road. On the 23rd of Sept, about nine o'clock, I was at home, and looking across the road, saw the prisoners loitering about the prosecutor's house—then Sheldon went in, and brought out the glass, which he gave to Jones, who waited outside—I came down stairs, crossed the road, and followed them—I took Sheldon, who then had the glass in his hand—he must have received it back from Jones while I came down stairs—I found them together—the prosecutor's man was at the back of the shop.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18431023-name-151" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-151" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-151" type="surname" value="BRIGHTMAN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-151" type="given" value="WILLIAM JOHN"></interp>WILLIAM JOHN BRIGHTMAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I am servant to Edward John Gairdner, who keeps an open broker's shop in Tottenham-court-road. This is his glass, and was in the shop.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18431023-name-152" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-152" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-152" type="surname" value="QUARY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18431023-name-152" type="given" value="DAVID"></interp>DAVID QUARY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman.</hi>) I took him in charge.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Jones's Defence.</hi> I met this lad; he said he was going to look for a situ<lb></lb>ation; I went with him; he went into the shop. I was not aware of his taking the glass.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Sheldon's Defence.</hi> I was at work with my father, and went to look after a place; this roan persuaded me to take the glass; if it had not been for him, I should not have done it.</p>
               <p>
